snippet.textDisplay: Many outbursts of anger against rotting vegetables and other seemingly minor issues are due to the fact the people have no influence on government policies such as the lock down. They know if they openly doubt or against the lockdown in general, their voice will be muted and they could end up in jail. So they vent their frustration on small specific errors that low level officials make.
